*   **[Foggy Bottom–GWU](/Foggy_Bottom%E2%80%93GWU_station)** (C04)
*   **[Farragut West](/Farragut_West_station)** (C03): Offers a walking transfer to the [Red Line](/Red_Line_(Washington_Metro)) at [Farragut North](/Farragut_North_station), branded as "Farragut Crossing."
